          published in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1991</TIMEX>, [ <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">4</ENAMEX> ] which used a extensive search
          strategy for <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Medline</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Embase</ENAMEX> <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">up to 1990</TIMEX>; <ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">2</ENAMEX>) a direct
          search of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Medline</ENAMEX> from <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1966 to August 1995</TIMEX> using the full
          text terms homeop*, homoeop*, and the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Mesh</ENAMEX> terms
