          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">homeopathic</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">researchers</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">institutions</ENAMEX> reporting on
          homeopathic research, homeopathic <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">manufacturers</ENAMEX> and
