          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Medline</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Embase</ENAMEX> from <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1989 to October 1995</TIMEX>. We
          operationally defined homeopathic research as studies
          involving <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">serially</ENAMEX> prepared dilutions selected according
